dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile shows areas of sand beaches in Kenya. This data layer was extracted from FAO's Africover dataset (2000).This data was used in Map 6.4 and Map 6.5 in Nature's Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being.
